Description: Yato is a god without a shrine. Or any worshippers for that matter. So, in order to build a lavish temple in his own honor, he takes on odd jobs and helps those in need for a nominal fee.
Title: NORAGAMI, VOL. 1
Author: Adachitoka

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Eren is free from the clutches of the Titans, but now he must learn to control a newly manifested power.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 13
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 4
Author: Okayado

Description: The terraforming of Mars has unforeseen consequences for humanity and for members of the various expeditions that investigate the methods used to change the planet in this futuristic series.
Title: TERRA FORMARS, VOL. 2
Author: Yu Sasuga and Kenichi Tachibana
Contributor: by Yu Sasuga and Kenichi Tachibana

Description: A new Turbo Duel hero named Yusei Fudo emerges from the outskirts of New Domino City and he will defeat any challenger thanks to his custom-built Duel Runner.
Title: YU-GI-OH! 5D'S, VOL. 6
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato
Contributor: by Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: The origins of the Survey Corps leaders Levi and Erwin are told in this spinâ€“off series.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN: NO REGRETS, VOL. 1
Author: Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama
Contributor: by Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama

Description: Princess Elizabeth continues her quest to reclaim her kingdom by finding the Seven Deadly Sins, a group of warriors who were wrongly sent into exile and branded as traitors.
Title: THE SEVEN DEADLY SINS, VOL. 4
Author: Nakaba Suzuki

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, the Titans attack and one of them goes rogue.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2
Author: Hajime Isayama
